HEADWORD: Worshiper
<hw>Wor"ship*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who worships;
one who pays divine honors to any being or thing; one who adores.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>worshipper</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

